This doc is based on Ubuntu server 12.04.1 LTS x86_64 system. 
Before compile login_checker, you must install this packages.

sudo apt-get install ia32-libs lib32gcc1 lib32stdc++6 libc6-dev-i386 gcc-multilib
sudo apt-get install swig
sudo apt-get install python2.7

optional:
	Install cryptopp.
		how to istall cryptopp.
			1. cd ../cryptopp
			2. ./configure
			3. make
			4. sudo make install		-- this is option.

If any packages or libs needs to install this packages or compile login_checker exist, 
   please install the packages or libs manually.

